[[include :scp-wiki:component:croqstyle -=- ]]
[[module css]]
.croqstyle__documentation :is(h1, h2) {
  font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.croqstyle__documentation h1 ~ h1 { margin-top: 6rem }
.croqstyle__documentation h1 ~ h2 { margin-top: 3rem }

.croqstyle__documentation #toc,
.croqstyle__description {
  border: thin solid #ddd;
  padding: 1em;
  background-color: transparent;
}

/* Don't show it on this page to stop people clicking on the broken links */
.earthworm { display: none }
[[/module]]

[[div class="croqstyle__description"]]
Earthworm Series Navigator is a decent-looking navigator for any series of articles, originally created by [[*user Croquembouche]] for the 2018 Doomsday contest.

It looks like this:

[[=image https://i.imgur.com/ZVOFu08.png]]

Don't like worms? Check out the [[[component:advanced-navigation-toolbar|ANT Series Navigator]]]!
[[/div]]

[[div class="croqstyle__documentation"]]
+ Usage

On any wiki:

[[div class="code terminal"]]
##var(--c-keyword)|[[####var(--c-operator)|include## ##var(--c-value)|:scp-wiki:component:earthworm##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|previous-url## ##var(--c-keyword)|=## ##var(--c-symbol)|URL_OF_PREVIOUS##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|previous-title## ##var(--c-keyword)|=## ##var(--c-string)|Title of previous page##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|next-url## ##var(--c-keyword)|=## ##var(--c-symbol)|URL_OF_NEXT##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|next-title## ##var(--c-keyword)|=## ##var(--c-string)|Title of text page##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|hub-url## ##var(--c-keyword)|=## ##var(--c-symbol)|URL_OF_HUB##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|hub-title## ##var(--c-keyword)|=## ##var(--c-string)|Title of hub page##
##var(--c-keyword)|]]##
[[/div]]

You should have up to 3 articles that you need to link to:
# The previous article in the series.
# The next article in the series.
# The hub page for the series.

(If you need more, e.g. splitting into 2 branches, [[[component:advanced-navigation-toolbar | ANT Series Navigator]]] might have you covered.)

For these examples, let's pretend you are adding Earthworm to SCP-002. Your previous page is SCP-001, then next page is SCP-003, and the hub page is SCP Series 1.

++ Previous page

**If there is a previous page:**

Replace {{URL_OF_PREVIOUS}} with the URL for the previous page in the series. You can use the full URL, {{@@https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-001@@}}, or just the slug, {{scp-001}}.

Replace {{Title of previous page}} with the title of the previous page.

**If there isn't (i.e. this is the first page in the series):**

Disable the previous page link by setting its URL to {{/}} //(i.e. {{previous-url=/}})//. The title will show as plain text. If you don't want any text, omit the {{previous-title}} field or leave it empty.

++ Next page

**If there is a next article:**

Replace {{URL_OF_NEXT}} with the URL for the next page in the series. You can use the full URL, {{@@https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-003@@}}, or just the slug, {{scp-003}}.

Replace {{Title of next page}} with the title of the next page.

**If there isn't (i.e. this is the last page in the series):**

Disable the next page link by setting its URL to {{/}} //(i.e. {{next-url=/}})//. The title will show as plain text (e.g. "Coming soon..."). If you don't want any text, omit the {{next-title}} field or leave it empty.

++ Hub page

**If there is a hub page:**

Replace {{URL_OF_HUB}} with the URL for the hub of the series. You can use the full URL, {{@@https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-series-1@@}}, or just the slug, {{scp-series-1}}.

Replace {{Title of hub page}} with the title of the hub page.

**If there isn't a hub page:**

Disable the hub page link by setting its URL to {{/}} //(i.e. {{hub-url=/}})//. The title will show as plain text. If you don't want any text, set the title to {{/}} as well, but the little box in the middle of the earthworm will still appear.

[[div class="croqstyle__description"]]
+ Examples

++ Page in the middle of a series

[[=image earthworm-example-middle.png]]

[[div class="code terminal"]]
##var(--c-keyword)|[[####var(--c-operator)|include## ##var(--c-value)|:scp-wiki:component:earthworm##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|previous-url####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-symbol)|scp-001##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|previous-title####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-string)|SCP-001##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|next-url####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-symbol)|scp-003##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|next-title####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-string)|SCP-003##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|hub-url####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-symbol)|scp-series-1##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|hub-title####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-string)|SCP Series 1##
##var(--c-keyword)|]]##
[[/div]]

++ Page at the start of a series

[[=image earthworm-example-start.png]]

[[div class="code terminal"]]
##var(--c-keyword)|[[####var(--c-operator)|include## ##var(--c-value)|:scp-wiki:component:earthworm##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|previous-url####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-symbol)|/##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|next-url####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-symbol)|introductory-antimemetics##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|next-title####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-string)|Introductory Antimemetics##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|hub-url####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-symbol)|antimemetics-division-hub##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|hub-title####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-string)|Antimemetics Division##
##var(--c-keyword)|]]##
[[/div]]

++ Page at the end of a series, with a teaser for more

[[=image earthworm-example-end-teaser.png]]

[[div class="code terminal"]]
##var(--c-keyword)|[[####var(--c-operator)|include## ##var(--c-value)|:scp-wiki:component:earthworm##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|previous-url####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-symbol)|a-gullet-made-of-the-flesh-of-a-swan##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|previous-title####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-string)|A Gullet, Made of the Flesh of a Swan##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|next-url####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-symbol)|/##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|next-title####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-string)|Coming soon...##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|hub-url####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-symbol)|end-of-death-hub#lookout-281##
##var(--c-keyword)||## ##var(--c-builtin)|hub-title####var(--c-keyword)| = ####var(--c-string)|LOOKOUT 281##
##var(--c-keyword)|]]##
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
